        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Methane Emissions Research Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Environmental Protection Agency to conduct a methane research pilot study to quantify methane emissions from infrastructure used for the production, gathering and boosting, processing, transmission, and storage of oil and natural gas in the United States.</p>]]></text>
